column2: SELECT SPA.ra, SPA.dec, SPA.z, SPA.petroMag_u, SPA.petroMag_g, SPA.petromag_r, PA.fracDeV_r, FSP5G.logMass, Extra.sfr_tot_p5# into GU2#_hw2    from SpecPhotoAll as SPA, PhotoObjAll as PA, stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as FSP5G, galSpecExtra as Extra Where   SPA.class = &&& and SPA.z < # and SPA.specObjID = PA.specObjID and SPA.specObjID = FSP5G.specobjID and SPA.specObjID = Extra.specObjID
